{"tid":1453051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再藍絲黃絲dllm 大家瞓醒未","createTime":"2019-08-12T03:08:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T06:45:23.000Z","uid":272186,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"16a710d2641165065a5997fcf6f6370de0c2faad","tid":1453051,"uid":272186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:08:04.000Z","msg":"點解大家仲未擺脫到14年嘅藍絲黃絲嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">標籤</span>，畀個政府、建制索住來走<br />\n<br />\n721元朗事件，琴晚811嘅事全部都反映緊而家唔再淨係政治立場問題，而係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">道德、良知、價值觀問題</span></strong></span>，係一場人道危機<br />\n<br />\n對家已經做緊<span style=\"color: red;\">去人性化嘅手段/[red]，叫我地做曱甴，而我地仲係用黑警、黑社會，文宣都係好溫和講事實<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">以後所有文宣口號從呢刻開始都要用過街老鼠、垃圾屎、畜生形容佢地</span></span></strong>，重點係標籤佢地[red]無良知</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"709a803d8fe54654ed3e68788db9b0dbf6dcdece","tid":1453051,"uid":272186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:42:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"da7c7bd97ca386fc6c9bbdf6bf42da8b5f1a3c71","tid":1453051,"uid":272186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:42:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>721 831</strong></span>"},{"pid":"0cf4dc262adec09bb7b64ca31313f94bfb8e40bf","tid":1453051,"uid":272186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:43:13.000Z","msg":"撐政府都無良知"},{"pid":"4a04d096a3c23471d8823c64ffc77e1e627032ed","tid":1453051,"uid":272186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:43:35.000Z","msg":"撐克警都無良知"},{"pid":"152b00a68a50f0143ce21691cae92810fa44b1ce","tid":1453051,"uid":272186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:43:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>光</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"30eafd00b7